    {
      "id": "39",
      "name": "推薦角色",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 34,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Hu Tao_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "胡桃",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "胡桃的生命值是目前為止最高的，該武器的特效很適合胡桃的成長數值，同時與胡桃的四破天賦相輔相成，大幅增加半血以下胡桃的輸出能力，是現版本最適合胡桃的武器。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 51,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Xiao_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "魈",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "魈的突破可以增加暴擊率，很適合該武器的副詞綴。且魈開啟元素爆發期間會持續損失生命值，更容易觸發該武器的半血Buff。魈使用該武器時，隊伍中最好有護盾角色，否則在高壓環境（如深淵）的情況下，觸發了半血Buff的狀況下魈的生命值會比較危險。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 46,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Zhongli_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "鍾離",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器比較適合在隊伍中擔任副C與盾輔助的鍾離。鍾離自身血量較高，該武器的技能增加血量的同時，也彌補了鍾離白攻較低的缺點，且鍾離自身能產生護盾，即使是處在半血狀態下，也有較好的輸出環境。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "其他任意輸出型長槍角色：該武器能提供高額",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "暴擊傷害",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "加成，武器特效還可以獲得生命值和攻擊力加成，對大部分輸出型長槍角色都是個不錯的選擇。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
